divs: sighting detailsi was taking the dog out and having a smoke with my neighbor and brother. i noticed the light when i first got outside. it was in the west\south west direction. i figured it was jupiter or a helicopter. -i had found jupiter, so i asked to 2 with me to see what it may be. after observing it for a minute, it moved so slowly, everyone thought "ufo". i grabbed my camera and got about 6-7 minutes of the object. it slowly moved left to right and descended slowly. it had a pulsating red\green light, but the main light was white. we watched it until it dropped behind the building next to us. i am trying to upload the video, but have had issues.
Summary: Saw bright light move slowly left to right, then descending
